"Uh....I've only seen rare pictures of you....I was originally from 
the original War on Cybertron, so if you had an impact on history 
after than, than forget it cause I went straight from their to here. 
But I was doing Autobot history the other day and a picture of you 
came up. Prime, is it? Rodimus Prime? No, That was the orange guy. 
Prime...Prime...Optimus Prime! That's gotta be your name. Optimus 
prime.
